				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Style Mantra is an online learning platform born out of a legacy in skill development and professional training.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Backed by over 11 years of experience through our parent company- Skills Mantra, we’ve successfully not just delivered high-impact skill training and assessments across various industries but have also generated employment for over 50,000/- learners. With a strong foundation in empowering learners and shaping careers, Style Mantra is a natural extension of our passion for creating meaningful, industry-relevant education with a focus on the ever-evolving world of fashion styling.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At Style Mantra, we bring the same dedication, structure, and learner-first approach that has been the hallmark of Skills Mantra. Our platform is designed to help aspiring stylists, fashion enthusiasts, and creative professionals master the art and science of styling, right from understanding body types and creating visual illusions to editorial styling and personal shopping.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We believe that style is more than fashion—it’s about expression, identity, and confidence. Our courses combine expert instruction, practical insights, and real-world techniques to help learners turn their passion for fashion into a thriving career or personal transformation.</span></p>								</div>
